JavaScript (ECMAScript/ES)

Web programming language appeared in 1995

- Front end- predomina in front end
- Back end- aici predomină mai puțin
- General Purpose(scop general-aplicatii web, mobile, extensii browser)

HTML-structura
CSS- stil, stilizare
JS- logică si comportament

Domenii de aplicare(Front End)
- interactivity
- dynamic content
- data processing
- data exchange
- effects
- animations
- etc ...


Biblioteci front end:
jquery
Vue, react, angular, ...


## General Aspects

* Dynamic typed
* Functional programming
* Object orient programming
* prototyping
* scrierea codului structurat- constructii speciale
* ...